    • Constructor Detail

      • SimpleResourceProviderMetadata

        public SimpleResourceProviderMetadata(String id,
                              String name,
                              String description,
                              Class<? extends ResourceProvider<?,?>> providerClass,
                              List<ConfigurationProperty> providerConfigurationProperties,
                              List<ConfigurationProperty> resourceTemplateConfigurationProperties,
                              List<DisplayProperty> resourceDisplayProperties)
        Creates an abstract resource provider metadata with the specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        id - the unique identifier of the provider within its scope
        name - the name of the provider, suitable for display in a drop-down menu of peer providers within the same scope
        description - the human-readable description of the provider
        providerClass - the resource provider class
        providerConfigurationProperties - the list of configuration properties that can be given to configure the provider
        resourceTemplateConfigurationProperties - the list of configuration properties that can be given to configure resources provided by the provider
        resourceDisplayProperties - the list of display properties present on resources provided by the provider
